            "For equal rise/fall: W_p/W_n = μ_n/μ_p",
            "Power: P = C_L×V_DD²×f (dynamic)"
          ],
          "formula": "τ = (C_L×V_DD)/I_D(sat)"
        },
        {
          "title": "Layout Area for Transistor",
          "steps": [
            "A = (W+L)×(feature size)²",
            "Feature size = minimum gate length L_min",
            "Contact area adds overhead",
            "Standard cell: fixed height, variable width",
