            "t_high = 0.693(R₁+R₂)C",
            "t_low = 0.693R₂C",
            "Duty cycle = (R₁+R₂)/(R₁+2R₂)",
            "For 50%: R₁ << R₂"
          ],
          "formula": "f = 1.44/((R₁+2R₂)C)"
        },
        {
          "title": "555 Monostable Pulse Width",
          "steps": [
            "T = 1.1×R×C (one-shot pulse)",
            "Trigger pulse < T (shorter than output)",
            "Pulse width independent of trigger width",
            "Retriggerable: trigger during pulse extends T",
            "Non-retriggerable: ignores subsequent triggers"
